statusDetails.message:
More than one Cucumber ObjectFactory was found on the classpath

Found: io.cucumber.spring.SpringFactory, io.cucumber.picocontainer.PicoFactory

You may have included, for instance, cucumber-spring AND cucumber-guice as part
of your dependencies. When this happens, Cucumber can't decide which to use.
In order to enjoy dependency injection features, either remove the unnecessary
dependencies from your classpath or use the `cucumber.object-factory` property
or `@CucumberOptions(objectFactory=...)` to select one.
